  <div class="card-body">
    <p>The OpenSplitTime API follows the JSON API standard, described in detail
      at <%= link_to 'jsonapi.org', 'https://jsonapi.org', target: '_blank' %>. You can query for a collection of
      records using the pluralized model name, and if you have an individual record id, you can query for an individual
      record.</p>
