  <h4 class="card-header">Standard Index Queries</h4>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>The primary models in use in OpenSplitTime are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Organization</li>
      <li>Course</li>
      <li>Split</li>
      <li>Event Group</li>
      <li>Event</li>
      <li>Effort</li>
      <li>Split Time</li>
      <li>Raw Time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Query any of these models by passing a GET request to the applicable endpoint. For example (you will need to
      replace the <code>xxxx</code> with your own JSON Web Token):</p>
    <hr/>
    <code>$ curl -H "Authorization: bearer xxxx" https://www.opensplittime.org/api/v1/events</code>
